&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create personal relationships with like-minded, hardworking professionals from the Volunteer Programme and from the Presidents Summit team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exclusive access to the official 2025 Presidents Summit Volunteer After Party for all members of the Volunteer Programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The conference will take place on the 10th and 11th June in Copenhagen.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
